uot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlta%20was%20founded%20in%202023%20by%20Neumark-Levi%2C%20a%20former%20Monday.com%20growth%20leader%2C%20alongside%20Tom%20Hoffen%20and%20Mor%20Shabtai%2C%20who%20previously%20sold%20his%20startup%2C%20Xperiti%2C%20to%20Ipsos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20says%20it%20worked%20with%20over%20100%20companies%20for%20over%20a%20year%20to%20analyze%20sales%20data%20and%20identify%20bottlenecks.%20The%20company%20used%20these%20findings%20to%20build%20an%20AI%20%26quot%3Bworkforce%26quot%3B%20that%20automates%20prospecting%2C%20research%2C%20outreach%2C%20and%20meeting%20scheduling%20while%20integrating%20with%20existing%20sales%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20a%20single%20AI%20assistant%2C%20Alta%20created%20a%20team%20of%20specialized%20agents.%20%26quot%3BKatie%26quot%3B%20handles%20prospecting%2C%20%26quot%3BLuna%26quot%3B%20manages%20revenue%20operations%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BAlex%26quot%3B%20follows%20up%20with%20leads%20and%20books%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlta's%20AI%20workforce%20aims%20to%20free%20sales%20teams%20from%20repetitive%20tasks.%20%26quot%3BSales%20teams%20are%20stuck%20spending%20hours%20on%20admin%20%E2%80%94%20copy-pasting%20messages%2C%20searching%20for%20the%20right%20lead%2C%20digging%20through%20outdated%20CRMs%2C%26quot%3B%20Neumark-Levi%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20surprise%20that%2070%25%20of%20their%20time%20isn't%20actually%20spent%20selling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlta's%20proprietary%20large%20language%20model%20powers%20its%20AI%20agents%20and%20integrates%20with%20over%2050%20business%20tools%2C%20including%20customer%20relationship%20management%20platforms%20like%20Salesforce%20and%20HubSpot%2C%20along%20with%20enterprise%20planning%20systems%2C%20payment%20tools%2C%20and%20social%20media%20platforms.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlta%20operates%20on%20a%20subscription%20model%2C%20with%20companies%20billed%20quarterly.%20Alta%20says%20it's%20already%20approaching%20100%20paying%20customers%2C%20including%20Fortune%20500%20companies%20and%20SMBs.%20Neumark-Levi%20plans%20to%20evolve%20this%20to%20an%20outcome-based%20pricing%20model%20based%20on%20meetings%20booked%20or%20revenue%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlta's%20%247%20million%20seed%20round%20was%20led%20by%20Entr%C3%A9e%20Capital%20and%20Target%20Global.%20Angel%20investor%20Ben%20Lang%20participated%2C%20as%20did%20a%20group%20of%20high-profile%20strategic%20advisors%2C%20including%20Gavin%20Patterson%2C%20the%20former%20president%20of%20Salesforce%2C%20Nir%20Goldstein%20of%20Greenfield%20Partners%2C%20and%20Yoram%20Teitz%20of%20General%20Atlantic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20caught%20our%20attention%20about%20Alta%20was%20how%20they've%20redefined%20the%20relationship%20between%20AI%20and%20sales%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shmuel%20Chafets%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Target%20Global.%20%26quot%3BRather%20than%20promising%20to%20replace%20humans%2C%20they've%20created%20AI%20team%20members%20that%20handle%20the%20heavy%20lifting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20fresh%20funding%2C%20Alta%20plans%20to%20expand%20beyond%20automating%20sales%20development%20representatives%20and%20create%20AI%20for%20account%20executives%20and%20account%20managers%2C%20bringing%20automation%20deeper%20into%20the%20sales%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20out%20the%2017-slide%20pitch%20deck%20Alta%20used%20to%20raise%20its%20%247%20million%20seed%20round.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224017%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alta%20slide%201%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c5bc2cb1834fe31165f1e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222267%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlta%3Cp%3EAlta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224017%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alta%20p2%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c5bc4f69253ccddf981022%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%