0like%20cross-border%20shipping%2C%20order%20tracking%2C%20return%20management%2C%20and%20inventory%20forecasting%2C%20Swap%20cofounder%20Sam%20Atkinson%20told%20BI.%20Swap%20brings%20all%20of%20these%20functions%20together%20into%20a%20single%20system%2C%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20multiple%20service%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20advantage%20there%20is%20that%20we%20get%20to%20consolidate%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20data%20that%20you%20get%20from%20these%20different%20products%20and%20different%20consumer%20interactions%2C%26quot%3B%20Atkinson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20supporting%20brands%20through%20the%20whole%20lifecycle%20%E2%80%94%20from%20when%20a%20product%20is%20going%20to%20be%20bought%20by%20the%20brand%20to%20when%20it%20is%20sold%20to%20the%20customer%20to%20when%20it's%20returned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwap%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-shop-ai-transformed-e-commerce-landscape-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintegrating%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20its%20platform%20to%20enhance%20its%20inventory%20management%20and%20operational%20processes.%20The%20company's%20newest%20product%2C%20Swap%20Inventory%2C%20will%20use%20AI%20to%20help%20clients%20forecast%20trends%20and%20demand%20by%20analyzing%20data%20from%20brands'%20warehouses%2C%20Shopify%20stores%2C%20and%20return%20data%20from%20its%20own%20platform.%20The%20company%20also%20uses%20AI%20to%20help%20with%20cross-border%20tax%20filing%20and%20return%20processing.%20Swap%20is%20using%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20different%20foundation%20models%26quot%3B%20for%20its%20AI%20products%2C%20including%20Claude%2C%20Gemini%2C%20and%20ChatGPT%2C%20Atkinson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwap's%20%26quot%3Bsweet%20spot%26quot%3B%20customers%20are%20brands%20generating%20between%20%245%20million%20and%20%24100%20million%20in%20revenue%2C%20Atkinson%20said.%20With%20the%20new%20funding%2C%20the%20company%20aims%20to%20expand%20to%20serve%20larger%20customers%20gradually.%20Swap's%20current%20clients%20include%20fashion%20labels%20Nadine%20Merabi%2C%20Motel%20Rocks%2C%20and%20The%20Frankie%20Shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20cofounding%20Swap%2C%20Atkinson%20worked%20as%20a%20corporate%20lawyer%20and%20at%20business%20banking%20startup%20Juni.%20Atkinson%20met%20cofounder%20Zach%20Bailet%20at%20business%20school%20and%20started%20another%20e-commerce%20company%20with%20him%20before%20cofounding%20Swap.%20Bailet%20previously%20worked%20at%20Deloitte%20and%20Tefron%2C%20a%20textile%20manufacturing%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20funding%20will%20support%20the%20120-person%20company's%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20helping%20brands%20sell%20internationally%2C%20Atkinson%20said.%20The%20platform%20assists%20with%20international%20sales%20by%20calculating%20duties%20and%20taxes%20at%20checkout%2C%20allowing%20customers%20to%20prepay%20these%20costs%20and%20avoid%20unexpected%20fees%20after%20delivery.%20Swap%20also%20uses%20AI%20to%20help%20brands%20determine%20international%20pricing%20strategies%20and%20partners%20with%20FedEx%20to%20manage%20international%20shipping%20for%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20capital%20will%20also%20help%20Swap%20expand%20into%20international%20markets%20such%20as%20Australia%2C%20Europe%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20the%20US.%20The%20startup%20is%20using%20the%20funding%20to%20build%20out%20its%20sales%20team%20and%20open%20a%20fourth%20office%20in%20New%20York%20this%20year.%20Swap%20already%20has%20offices%20in%20London%2C%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20and%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20rivals%20a%20range%20of%20companies%20in%20the%20e-commerce%20logistics%20space.%20Its%20cross-border%20product%20competes%20with%20Global-E%2C%20a%20public%20company%20that%20also%20provides%20tools%2C%20like%20duties%20and%20tax%20calculations%2C%20that%20help%20brands%20sell%20their%20products%20internationally.%20Swap's%20inventory%20management%20software%20goes%20up%20against%20companies%20such%20as%20Syrup%20and%20Autone%2C%20which%20both%20also%20offer%20AI-based%20forecasting%20for%20merchandising%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20small%20merchants%20have%20to%20cobble%20together%20a%20handful%20of%20tools%20in%20order%20to%20solve%20all%20their%20operational%20challenges%20end%20to%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Seth%20Pierrepont%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20at%20ICONIQ%20Growth%20based%20in%20London%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BSwap%20took%20a%20very%20different%20view%20to%20that.%20They're%20like%2C%20'we're%20going%20to%20solve%20it%20all%20in%20one%20single%20platform.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswap-secures-funding-streamline-e-commerce-logistics-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741089601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c61cfc69253ccddf982557%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswap-secures-funding-streamline-e-commerce-logistics-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20%2440%20million%20in%20fresh%20funding%20led%20by%20ICONIQ%20Growth%2C%20Swap%20aims%20to%20enhance%20e-commerce%20logistics%20with%20AI%20and%20international%20market%20expansion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhornstein%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Hornstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswap-secures-funding-streamline-e-commerce-logistics-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Supernatural%2C%E2%80%99%20About%20Shaman%20and%20His%20Skeptical%20Son%2C%20Acquired%20by%20Taskovski%20Ahead%20of%20Premiere%20at%20Thessaloniki%20Documentary%20Festival%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741089486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FSupern