%20by%20his%20father%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Lalu%20Prasad%20and%20slammed%20the%20regime%20led%20by%20his%20former%20ally%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20face-off%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20leader%20sneered%20at%20the%20budget%20presented%20by%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government.%C2%A0Terming%20the%20budget%20%26quot%3Binflated%26quot%3B%20and%20drafted%20with%20%26quot%3Bink%20dipped%20in%20lies%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20strange%20that%20despite%20no%20revenue%20generation%2C%20the%20size%20of%20the%20budget%20keeps%20increasing.%20The%20figure%20of%20Rs%203.71%20lakh-crore%20is%20highly%20inflated.%20The%20budget%20papers%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20written%20with%20ink%20dipped%20in%20lies.%20They%20could%20have%20made%20it%20Rs%205%20lakh-crore%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%20has%20been%20constant%20in%20his%20attack%20on%20Nitish%20Kumar%20since%20their%20alliance%20snapped%20in%202024.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20he%20mocked%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20government%20in%20Bihar%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20time%20has%20come%20to%20change%20the%20two-decade-old%20dispensation%2C%20much%20like%2015-year-old%20vehicles%20are%20banned%20in%20the%20state%20for%20spreading%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%2020-year-old%20NDA%20government%20in%20Bihar%2C%20headed%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20has%20now%20turned%20into%20a%20rickety%20vehicle.%20There%20is%20a%20ban%20on%20vehicles%20that%20are%20more%20than%2015%20years%20old%20across%20Bihar%20as%20they%20emit%20too%20much%20smoke%2C%20increase%20pollution%20and%20are%20harmful%20to%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%2C%20also%20the%20JD(U)%20chief%2C%20had%20ended%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%202013%2C%20only%20to%20return%20four%20years%20later%2C%20after%20having%20shared%20power%20with%20the%20RJD%20between%202015%20and%202017.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20again%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20RJD-helmed%20'Mahagathbandhan'%20but%20was%20back%20in%20the%20NDA%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741088100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fb22ecjbg_nitish-kumar_625x300_27_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumars-big-attack-on-tejashwi-yadav-lalu-prasad-i-made-your-father-7845719%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bihar%20assembly%20witnessed%20a%20bitter%20exchange%20between%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20his%20former%20deputy-turned-rival%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumars-big-attack-on-tejashwi-yadav-lalu-prasad-i-made-your-father-7845719%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20On%20Imtiaz%20Ali's%2020%20Years%2C%20A%20Tribute%20To%20His%20OG%20'Rockstar'%2C%20Aarti%20Bajaj%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20Imtiaz%20Ali%20opening%20feels%20like%20its%20own%20genre.%20Each%20feels%20sharper%20than%20the%20last%20until%20you%20circle%20back%20and%20realise%20the%20older%20one%20never%20stopped%20breathing.%20But%20revisit%20the%20new%20again%2C%20and%20it%20opens%20up%2C%20revealing%20something%20you%20missed.%20This%20cycle%20goes%20on%2C%20and%20it%20will%2C%20as%20long%20as%20there%20are%20movies%20and%20as%20long%20as%20Ali%20keeps%20pulling%20us%20under%20in%20those%20first%20few%20moments%3A%20where%20life%20isn't%20just%20shown%2C%20it%20spills%20over.%20With%20his%20longtime%2C%20glorious%20editor%20Aarti%20Bajaj%2C%20he%20doesn't%20just%20set%20the%20tone.%20They%20stretch%20the%20form%2C%20dragging%20you%20into%20the%20mess%20and%20ache%20of%20being%20alive.%20Yet%2C%20beneath%20that%20mastery%2C%20there's%20a%20sense%20that%20they%2C%20too%2C%20are%20caught.%20There's%20a%20sense%20that%20they%2C%20too%2C%20are%20swept%20away%20by%20the%20same%20wild%20currents%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20screen.%20There's%20a%20sense%20that%20they%20are%20chasing%20something%20cinema%20can%20barely%20contain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShock%2C%20Grief%2C%20Awe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20%3Cem%3EAmar%20Singh%20Chamkila's%3C%2Fem%3E%20opening.%20It%20doesn't%20just%20shock%2C%20it%20shakes%20you%20loose.%20First%2C%20there's%20the%20killing.%20Chamkila%20(Diljit%20Dosanjh)%20and%20Amarjot%20(Parineeti%20Chopra)%20gunned%20down%20in%20broad%20daylight.%20But%20before%20the%20weight%20of%20their%20death%20settles%2C%20the%20screen%20slips%20into%20black%20and%20white.%20Chamkila%2C%20now%20dressed%20in%20ethereal%20white%2C%20stands%20like%20a%20ghostly%20troubadour%20%E2%80%94%20performing%2C%20perhaps%2C%20in%20some%20imagined%20heaven.%20Just%20as%20you%20begin%20to%20grasp%20this%20surreal%20farewell%2C%20Bajaj's%20cut%20hurls%20you%20back%20%E2%80%94%20to%20a%20young%20Chamkila%2C%20wide-eyed%2C%20absorbing%20the%20rawness%20of%20the%20world%20around%20him.%20And%20then%2C%20without%20warning%2C%20you%20return%20to%20the%20aftermath.%20Their%20lifeless%20bodies%20sprawled%20like%20casualties%20of%20a%20war%20no%20one%20saw%20coming.%20It's%20a%20battlefield%20frozen%20in%20shock%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20silence%20Kurosawa%20once%20captured.%20Grief%20looms%20in%20the%20air%2C%20and%20those%20who%20witnessed%20it%20cower%20unseen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F7tdkqsmg_amar-singh-chamkila_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Csmall%3EA%20still%20from%20%3Cem%3EAmar%20Singh%20Chamkila%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Bajaj%20doesn't%20stop.%20The%20rhythm%20shifts%20again.%20Mohit%20Chauhan%20steps%20into%20the%20frame%2C%20breaks%20the%20fourth%20wall%2C%20and%20with%20a%20sly%20smile%2C%20begins%20%E2%80%98Baaja'.%20Suddenly%2C%20the%20tone%20turns%20playful%20and%20cheekier%2C%20unburdened%20by%20reverence.%20All%20of%20Punjab%20bursts%20into%20the%20song.%20Rival%20singers%2C%20truck%20drivers%2C%20schoolgirls%2C%20hockey%20players.%20Each%20voice%20passing%20the%20tune%20like%20a%20Chinese%20whisper.%20And%20as%20expected%2C%20the%20innovation%20doesn't%20stop%20either.%20The%20screen%20fractures%20into%20split%20frames.%20Archival%20footage%20bleeds%20into%20animation.%20Intertitles%20flash%20across%20the%20chaos.%20It's%20cinema%2C%20yes.%20But%20also%20something%20wilder%2C%20older%3F%20Like%20a%20Greek%20chorus%20echoing%20through%20time%3F%20Is%20this%20fiction%2C%20you%20think%3F%20Or%20nonfiction%3F%20Perhaps%2C%20hybrid%3F%20Nobody%20knows.%20Maybe%20even%20Bajaj%20and%20Ali%20wouldn't%20dare%20to%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20Writes%2C%20Other%20Rewrites%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20is%20potent%20for%20many%20reasons.%20Chief%20among%20them%20is%20how%20vividly%20it%20captures%20the%20magic%20that%20happens%20when%20Ali%20and%20Bajaj%20come%20together%20to%20tell%20a%20story.%20It%20also%20makes%20one%20thing%20undeniably%20clear%3A%20as%20Ali%20completes%2020%20years%20in%20the%20film%20industry%20(his%20debut%20%3Cem%3ESocha%20Na%20Tha%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereleased%20on%20March%204%2C%202005)%2C%20he%20remains%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20incomplete%20without%20Bajaj.%20Because%20his%20characters%20are%20such%20complex%20beasts%2C%20they%20can't%20just%20be%20written%3B%20they%20must%20be%20rewritten.%20And%20no%20one%20does%20that%20better%20than%20Bajaj.%20No%20one%20else%20could%20shape%20his%20wild%2C%20sprawling%20ideas%20with%20such%20clarity%20and%20abandon%20as%20her.%20And%20no%20one%20knows%20him%20as%20intimately%20as%20she%20does.%20But%20beyond%20their%20creative%20synergy%2C%20this%20opening%20distils%20the%20heart%20of%20their%20shared%20artistic%20pursuit%20%E2%80%94%20to%20tell%20stories%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20as%20layered%20and%20restless%20as%20life%20itself%2C%20refusing%20simplicity%2C%20embracing%20the%20mess%2C%20and%20finding%20truth%20in%20all%20its%20jagged%20edges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5fqcmvg_asc_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E(Diljit%20Dosanjh%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAmar%20Singh%20Chamkila%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20%3Cem%3EAmar%20Singh%20Chamkila%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20crafted%20like%20a%20folktale%2C%20woven%20from%20the%20many%20voices%20and%20pieces%20of%20a%20beloved%20yet%20controversial%20figure%2C%20the%20same%20holds%20true%20for%20how%20Bajaj%20and%20Ali%20approach%20their%20films.%20Their%20gaze%20is%20never%20fixed%3B%20it%20shifts%2C%20evolves%2C%20questions.%20It%20feels%20as%20though%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20understand%20their%20characters%20in%20real%20time.%20It%20feels%20as%20though%20they%20are%20grappling%20with%20their%20contradictions%20as%20they%20shape%20them.%20It%20feels%20as%20though%20in%20the%20editing%20room%2C%20this%20becomes%20an%20act%20of%20discovery%3A%20a%20process%20of%20mixing%2C%20matching%2C%20and%20throwing%20things%20at%20the%20screen%2C%20hoping%20to%20peel%20back%20the%20layers%20and%20see%20their%20subjects%20more%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20Coherence%20Eat%20Cake%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20way%2C%20it%20mirrors%20the%20essence%20of%20Ali's%20stories%20where%20love%20is%20not%20just%20a%20feeling%20but%20a%20test%2C%20something%20his%20characters%20must%20prove%20themselves%20worthy%20of.%20Similarly%2C%20through%20every%20frame%2C%20every%20cut%2C%20Bajaj%20and%20Ali%20seem%20to%20be%20proving%20to%20themselves%20that%20they%20are%20worthy%20of%20telling%20these%20stories.%20And%20in%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20seem%20indifferent%20to%20coherence%20or%20continuity.%20Whether%20it%20becomes%20difficult%20to%20follow%20or%20too%20much%20to%20take%20in%20is%20of%20little%20concern.%20Because%20they%20are%20not%20chasing%20clarity%3B%20they%20are%20searching%20for%20meaning.%20Their%20structures%20are%20non-linear%20not%20out%20of%20a%20narrative%20necessity%2C%20but%20from%20a%20deeper%2C%20more%20restless%20need%20to%20find%20the%20narrative%20itself%2C%20piece%20by%20piece.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20and%20space%E2%80%94the%20very%20anchors%20of%20cinematic%20storytelling%E2%80%94are%20tossed%20into%20the%20air%20by%20Bajaj.%20In%20her%20hands%2C%20they%20lose%20their%20grip%2C%20as%20timelines%20blur%20and%20spatial%20rules%20dissolve.%20Take%20%3Cem%3ELove%20Aaj%20Kal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20second%20collaboration%20between%20Bajaj%20and%20Ali.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20glimpse%20of%20their%20shared%20fascination%20with%20time's%20slipperiness.%20The%20film%20opens%20in%20London%3A%20two%20strangers%20share%20a%20lift%2C%20then%20a%20dance%2C%20then%20a%20kiss%20in%20a%20car.%20By%20the%20next%20day%2C%20they're%20following%20each%20other%20on%20social%20media.%20Soon%2C%20they're%20shopping%20together%2C%20falling%20into%20a%20relationship%20that%20stretches%20over%20a%20year.%20Smooth%20jump%20cuts%20and%20dissolves%20pulling%20us%20through%20their%20casual%20love.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Magic%20Of%20Sorts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20true%20sleight%20of%20hand%20arrives%20with%20the%20first%20song.%20As%20the%20credits%20roll%2C%20the%20film%20fractures.%20The%20couple%20reappears%20across%20different%20phases%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20scattered%20across%20cities%2C%20while%20another%20love%20story%20unfolds%20in%20sepia-toned%20memory.%20San%20Francisco's%20slick%20roads%20morph%20into%20Old%20Delhi's%20dusty%20lanes%3B%20the%20Golden%20Gate%20dissolves%20into%20the%20Howrah%20Bridge.%20It's%20the%20first%20Bajaj%20montage%20in%20an%20Ali%20film.%20She%20does%20something%20similar%20in%20the%20iconic%20opening%20montage%20of%20%3Cem%3ERockstar%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20begins%20with%20Jordan%20(Ranbir%20Kapoor)%2C%20poised%20to%20perform%20at%20his%20own%20concert.%20But%20before%20we%20can%20hear%20him%2C%20the%20film%20jumps%20into%20his%20past.%20We%20see%20him%20not%20as%20the%20brooding%20rockstar%20but%20as%20Janardhan%20Jakhar%3A%20wide-eyed%20and%20unpolished%2C%20auditioning%20for%20a%20college%20contest%2C%20singing%20the%20same%20song%20with%20the%20same%20aching%20voice.%20From%20there%2C%20the%20montage%20hurtles%20forward%2C%20glimpsing%20his%20evolution%E2%80%94performing%20in%20recording%20studios%2C%20clubs%2C%20and%20concert%20halls.%20He%20sings%20for%20those%20at%20%3Cem%3Edargahs%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ejagratas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20brothels%2C%20but%20also%20in%20solitude.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F6bv87rg8_rockstar_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%3E%3Csmall%3E(A%20still%20from%20%3Cem%3ERockstar%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fh4%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20hair%20grows%2C%20his%20beard%20thickens%2C%20his%20voice%20deepens.%20Each%20frame%20marks%20a%20change%2C%20a%20journey%20that%20the%20film%20will%20chase%2C%20not%20in%20order%2C%20but%20in%20ruptures.%20It%20is%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20a%20bold%20and%20defiant%20move.%20To%20reveal%20the%20very%20highlights%20the%20film%20will%20later%20explore%20in%20some%20detail.%20Indeed%2C%20this%20style%20mirrors%20the%20turbulence%20of%20Jordan's%20life%2C%20his%20contradictions%2C%20his%20restlessness.%20More%20than%20that%2C%20it%20signals%20a%20refusal%20to%20deliver%20a%20clean%2C%20coherent%20portrait.%20Instead%2C%20it%20offers%20fragments%2C%20leaving%20the%20audience%20to%20stitch%20together%20the%20man%20he%20becomes.%20But%20beneath%20this%20structural%20daring%20lies%20something%20deeper.%20A%20glimpse%20into%20Ali%20and%20Bajaj's%20enduring%20preoccupation%20with%20broken%20timelines%2C%20emotional%20truths%20over%20factual%20precision%2C%20reveals%20their%20belief%20that%20a%20person's%20essence%20cannot%20be%20captured%20through%20a%20neat%2C%20linear%20biography.%20Their%20cinema%20suggests%20that%20life%E2%80%94any%20life%E2%80%94cannot%20be%20told%20in%20order.%20It%20must%20be%20felt%20in%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ever-Stunning%20Drama%20In%20%3Cem%3ETamasha%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20playful%20disregard%20for%20space%2C%20there%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20magnetic%20%E2%80%98Heer%20Toh%20Badi%20Sad%20Hai'%20from%20%3Cem%3ETamasha%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Tara%20(Deepika%20Padukone)%20returns%20from%20Corsica%20to%20Kolkata%2C%20her%20hometown.%20But%20the%20song%20cuts%20elsewhere%2C%20unfolding%20in%20Punjab%2C%20where%20a%20band%20of%20%3Cem%3Esardars%20%3C%2Fem%3Eacts%20like%20a%20Greek%20chorus.%20It%20captures%20Tara's%20heartbreak%20across%20five%20years%20of%20a%20life%20dulled%20by%20routine.%20But%20underneath%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20Bajaj%20and%20Ali%20are%20asking%3A%20why%20should%20Tara%2C%20being%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20stop%20the%20song%20from%20playing%20in%20Punjab%3F%20Wasn't%20that%20where%20Heer%20was%20from%3F%20And%20aren't%20all%20stories%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20far%20apart%2C%20woven%20from%20the%20same%20longing%2C%20the%20same%20heartbreak%3F%20This%20question%20also%20forms%20the%20fundamental%20editing%20pattern%20of%20both%20the%20film%20and%20another%20stunning%20opening%E2%80%94%E2%80%98Chali%20Kahaani'%3A%20a%20seamless%20blend%20of%20fantasy%20and%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fa57dcuuo_tamasha_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E(A%20still%20from%20%3Cem%3ETamasha%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20young%20Ved%20(Yash%20Sehgal)%2C%20whose%20mind%20constantly%20mixes%20the%20mythical%20with%20the%20mundane.%20In%20his%20home%20and%20school%20corridors%2C%20he%20imagines%20Ram%20and%20Sita%2C%20Helen%20and%20Paris%2C%20Soni%20and%20Mahiwal.%20All%20these%20timeless%20lovers%20form%20his%20everyday%20world.%20Amid%20these%20visions%2C%20a%20fleeting%20glimpse%20of%20his%20future%20self%20(Ranbir%20Kapoor)%20also%20appears%E2%80%94yearning%2C%20while%20his%20Heer%2C%20Tara%2C%20waits%20quietly%20at%20a%20doorstep.%20His%20mind%20overflows%20with%20images%2C%20alive%20with%20imagination%20and%20a%20deep%20love%20for%20stories.%20And%20without%20realising%20it%2C%20he%20is%20already%20writing%20his%20own%20epic%2C%20one%20that%20will%20unravel%20in%20ways%20even%20he%20cannot%20yet%20comprehend.%20In%20a%20way%2C%20it's%20Bajaj%20and%20Ali%20teasing%20us%20again%E2%80%94not%20with%20where%20this%20story%20will%20eventually%20go%2C%20but%20with%20a%20bigger%20question%3A%20how%20will%20we%20get%20there%3F%20As%20with%20all%20great%20cinema%2C%20the%20journey%20matters%20more%20than%20the%20destination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMontages%2C%20But%20Not%20Really%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20opening%20also%20reveals%20something%20essential%20about%20their%20artistic%20method.%20Bajaj's%20editing%20often%20treats%20entire%20scenes%20like%20extended%20montages.%20But%20not%20in%20the%20conventional%20sense%20of%20classical%20Hollywood%20or%20d%C3%A9coupage.%20Her%20approach%20leans%20closer%20to%20the%20principles%20of%20Soviet%20montage%3A%20where%20meaning%20doesn't%20emerge%20from%20individual%20shots%20but%20from%20their%20collision.%20These%20juxtapositions%20are%20not%20seamless%20but%20confrontational%2C%20creating%20a%20dialectical%20tension%20where%20images%20clash%20in%20tone%2C%20continuity%2C%20and%20thematic%20weight.%20Because%20Bajaj%20isn't%20content%20with%20surface-level%20meaning.%20Her%20cuts%20seek%20a%20deeper%20resonance.%20They%20seek%20to%20move%20beyond%20the%20connotative%20(the%20literal%2C%20what%20is%20shown)%20to%20the%20denotative%20(the%20implied%2C%20what%20stays%20beneath).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENowhere%20is%20this%20more%20potent%20than%20in%20%3Cem%3EAmar%20Singh%20Chamkila's%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%98Ishq%20Mithaye'.%20The%20picturisation%20is%20replete%20with%20contradictions.%20Shots%20of%20riots%20and%20violence%20rub%20against%20images%20of%20people%20dancing%20at%20Chamkila's%20%3Cem%3Eakhadas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Even%20the%20lyrics%20symbolise%20this%20duality%E2%80%94%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EIshq%20Mithaye...%20Ishq%20Banaye%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(love%20that%20breaks%E2%80%A6love%20that%20makes).%20And%20then%20comes%20the%20line%20that%20haunts%20like%20a%20protest%20cry%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMain%20Hoon%20Punjab%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(I%20Am%20Punjab).%20It%20carries%20the%20same%20raw%2C%20defiant%20spirit%20as%20%E2%80%98Sadda%20Haq'%20from%20Rockstar.%20It's%20a%20profoundly%20self-aware%20moment.%20Both%20Chamkila%20and%20Jordan%20create%20art%20that%20inevitably%20becomes%20political%2C%20much%20like%20Bajaj%20and%20Ali%2C%20whose%20artistry%20is%20laced%20with%20a%20silent%20rebellion%2C%20revealing%20its%20politics%20when%20you%20least%20expect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Disorienting%20Leap%20In%20%3Cem%3ERockstar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20crucial%20aspect%20of%20Bajaj%20and%20Ali's%20storytelling%20is%20their%20tendency%20to%20return%20to%20the%20same%20visuals%20repeatedly.%20But%20each%20time%2C%20they%20reveal%20something%20deeper.%20Take%20%E2%80%98Phir%20Se%20Udd%20Chala'%20from%20%3Cem%3ERockstar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20for%20instance.%20The%20song%20erupts%20seemingly%20out%20of%20nowhere.%20Just%20moments%20ago%2C%20Jordan%20was%20in%20Kashmir%20at%20Heer's%20(Nargis%20Fakhri)%20wedding%2C%20and%20now%2C%20he's%20soaring%20on%20wings%20of%20fame.%20The%20sudden%20leap%20is%20disorienting%20on%20first%20viewing.%20But%20as%20the%20film%20revisits%20these%20images%20in%20their%20supposed%20continuity%2C%20a%20clearer%20truth%20emerges%E2%80%94Jordan%20isn't%20just%20ascending%20through%20stardom%2C%20he's%20transcending%20reality%20itself%2C%20propelled%20by%20a%20longing%20to%20return%20to%20Heer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F1ga5peg8_heer_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E(A%20still%20from%20the%20song%3Cem%3E%20'Heer%20To%20Badi%20Sad%20Hai'%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imagery%20isn't%20arbitrary.%20He%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Eparinda%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20is%20the%20bird%20with%20wings%20on%20fire%20(not%20coincidentally%2C%20it's%20also%20the%20name%20of%20his%20concert%20tour).%20This%20recurring%20motif%20suggests%20that%20his%20fame%20is%20not%20liberation%20but%20an%20affliction.%20His%20flight%20is%20not%20about%20escaping%20the%20past%20but%20circling%20back%20to%20the%20one%20thing%20he%20cannot%20let%20go%20of.%20And%20Bajaj%20is%20simply%20trying%20to%20capture%20this%20spirit%20through%20her%20transitions.%20This%20holds%20true%20for%20all%20of%20Ali's%20characters.%20They%20all%20are%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ebade%20janwar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(the%20wild%20beasts)%20who%20resist%20being%20tamed%20or%20contained.%20So%2C%20her%20editing%20doesn't%20attempt%20to%20confine%20them%3B%20instead%2C%20she%20tries%20to%20hold%20them%20still%2C%20if%20only%20for%20a%20moment%E2%80%94to%20understand%20them%20a%20little%20better.%20But%20just%20as%20quickly%2C%20she%20sets%20them%20free%20again%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20determine%20their%20own%20destinies.%20This%20instinct%20is%20perhaps%20most%20evident%20in%20the%20way%20she%20chooses%20to%20end%20an%20Ali%20film.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20The%20Characters%20Live%2C%20Love%2C%20Speak%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20seeks%20to%20bookend%20every%20Ali%20film%2C%20but%20not%20in%20the%20traditionally%20understood%20sense.%20If%20the%20opening%20mostly%20takes%20us%20through%20a%20character's%20destiny%20in%20highlights%2C%20the%20closing%20allows%20the%20character%20to%20navigate%20their%20own%20life%2C%20in%20its%20totality.%20If%20the%20opening%20is%20about%20Bajaj%20defining%20their%20lives%20through%20her%20cuts%3B%20the%20closing%20is%20about%20characters%20dictating%20what%20comes%20next.%20%3Cem%3ERockstar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20for%20instance.%20If%20the%20opening%20is%20all%20about%20Jordan's%20musical%20career%2C%20his%20art%20and%20his%20rise%20to%20fame%2C%20then%20the%20closing%20is%20about%20him%20as%20an%20artist%2C%20with%20his%20true%20muse%2C%20Heer%2C%20and%20his%20pursuit%20of%20love.%20Similarly%2C%20if%20the%20opening%20of%20%3Cem%3EAmar%20Singh%20Chamkila%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20filled%20with%20the%20voices%20of%20an%20entire%20Punjab%20offering%20their%20opinions%20about%20Chamkila%2C%20the%20closing%20is%20reserved%20for%20him%2C%20where%20he%20finally%20gets%20to%20share%20his%20thoughts%20on%20the%20listeners%20who%20never%20truly%20heard%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20in%20the%20closing%20bits%2C%20she%20grants%20her%20characters%20the%20power%20to%20rewrite%20their%20pasts.%20Sometimes%20in%20reality%2C%20like%20both%20versions%20of%20%3Cem%3ELove%20Aaj%20Kal%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Sometimes%20in%20imagination%2C%20like%20%3Cem%3ETamasha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20Ved%2C%20as%20both%20man%20and%20child%2C%20finally%20moves%20through%20his%20world%20unbound.%20It%20is%20very%20much%20like%20Jordan%3B%20he%20soars%20through%20corridors%2C%20and%20as%20Irshad%20Kamil%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EPurana%20bhi%2C%20naya%20bhi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(such%20that%20is%20old%2C%20and%20new%20too).%20In%20her%20own%20way%2C%20Bajaj%20honours%20this%20line%2C%20allowing%20the%20past%20and%20present%20to%20fold%20into%20each%20other.%20And%20it%20is%20in%20these%20songs%20where%20her%20craft%20sings%20the%20loudest.%20There%2C%20the%20rhythm%20becomes%20her%20language.%20This%20is%20why%20she%20works%20so%20seamlessly%20with%20Ali.%20Because%20there%20is%20always%20music%20in%20his%20frames%2C%20even%20when%20there%20isn't.%20Their%20stories%20are%20always%20the%20same%3B%20it%20is%20the%20two%20who%20keep%20changing%20with%20every%20film%2C%20trying%20to%20seek%20not%20only%20their%20characters%2C%20their%20stories%2C%20and%20but%20perhaps%20even%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anas%20Arif%20is%20a%20film%20writer%20and%20a%20media%20graduate%20from%20AJKMCRC%2C%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741087980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Firfknjk_ali_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-tribute-to-imtiaz-ali-and-his-real-rockstar-aarti-bajaj-7845671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20his%20longtime%2C%20glorious%20editor%20Aarti%20Bajaj%2C%20Ali%20doesn't%20just%20set%20the%20tone.%20The%20duo%20stretches%20the%20form%2C%20dragging%20you%20into%20the%20mess%20and%20ache%20of%20being%20alive.%20Yet%2C%20beneath%20that%20mastery%2C%20there's%20a%20sense%20that%20they%2C%20too%2C%20are%20caught.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-tribute-to-imtiaz-ali-and-his-real-rockstar-aarti-bajaj-7845671%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%