d%20a%20new%20state%20of%20matter%20to%20power%20its%20own%20new%20quantum%20chip%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eprototype%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMajorana%201%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20development%20that%20would%20propel%20quantum%20computing%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-unveiled-quantum-computer-chip-willow-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWillow%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E%20prototype%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edebuted%20in%20December.%20The%20company%20said%20Willow%20could%20perform%20a%20standard%20benchmark%20computation%20in%20under%20five%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20a%20task%20that%20would%20take%20the%20current%20fastest%20supercomputers%2010%20septillion%20years%20to%20complete%2C%20a%20timeframe%20that%20exceeds%20the%20age%20of%20the%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20giants%20say%20their%20respective%20developments%20are%20massive%20advancements%20in%20the%20quantum%20computing%20field%2C%20which%20could%20eventually%20lead%20to%20major%20social%20advancements%20such%20as%20discovering%20new%20drugs%2C%20developing%20new%20chemical%20compounds%2C%20or%20breaking%20our%20current%20encryption%20methods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20computer%20scientists%20and%20physicists%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20field%20remains%20dynamic%20and%20evolving%2C%20with%20hurdles%20to%20overcome%20before%20quantum%20computing%20is%20useful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aef61558-e189-4b23-9287-c7ed2eadb3db%5C%22%3E'The%20joke%20is%2C%20it's%20always%2025%20years%20away'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVirginia%20Lorenz%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20atomic%2C%20molecular%2C%20and%20optical%20physics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois'%20Grainger%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20said%20there%20are%20still%20many%20technical%20roadblocks%20in%20the%20way%20of%20fully%20functional%20and%20commercially%20relevant%20quantum%20computing%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fgoogle-googl-races-ahead-in-quantum-computing-partnering-with-promising-startups-1034373959%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equantum%20computers%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20do%20something%20useful%20for%20the%20average%20person%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20scientists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20joke%20is%2C%20it's%20always%2025%20years%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lorenz%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20first%20publicly%20available%20quantum%20network%2C%20which%20allows%20citizen%20scientists%20to%20experiment%20with%20the%20tech%20while%20visiting%20the%20Urbana%20Free%20Library.%20%26quot%3BAt%20least%20if%20you%20keep%20the%20current%20approaches%2C%20the%20problems%20are%20technical%2C%20and%20there%20are%20many%20of%20them%2C%20versus%20the%20situation%20being%20everyone%20trying%20different%20ways%20of%20solving%20one%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EQuantum%20computing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20field%20of%20technology%20that%20relies%20on%20units%20of%20information%20called%20qubits%20rather%20than%20the%20binary%20bits%20used%20in%20classical%20computing.%20Qubits%20exist%20in%20multiple%20states%20at%20once%20and%20require%20specific%20conditions%20such%20as%20low%20light%20or%20extremely%20cold%20environments%20to%20replicate%20results%20reliably%20and%20without%20errors%2C%20which%20has%20made%20advancement%20in%20the%20field%20slow%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eagree%20that%20the%20two%20main%20roadblocks%20to%20advancing%20the%20quantum%20field%20lie%20in%20scalability%20and%20error%20correction.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20no%20consensus%20about%20how%20to%20approach%2C%20much%20less%20solve%2C%20either%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20February%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fgoogle-says-commercial-quantum-computing-applications-arriving-within-five-years-2025-02-05%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20release%20commercial%20quantum%20computing%20applications%20within%20five%20years%2C%20despite%20skepticism%20from%20some%20industry%20insiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Google%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they're%20confident%20in%20their%20approach%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-google-quantum-willow-chip-breakthrough-big-deal-researchers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20company's%20projected%20timeline%20for%20commercial%20quantum%20applications.%20However%2C%20they%20added%20that%20it's%20important%20to%20discern%20between%20what%20a%20company%20describes%20as%20a%20breakthrough%20and%20what%20the%20broader%20quantum%20community%20considers%20a%20breakthrough%2C%20highlighting%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20peer-review%20publication%20processes%20of%20scientific%20journals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20tech%20giants%20have%20made%20some%20strides%20in%20showing%20progress%20on%20the%20error%20reduction%20and%20scalability%20issues%20using%20various%20approaches%2C%20quantum%20technology%20experts%20told%20BI%20they%20haven't%20come%20close%20to%20solving%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETroy%20Nelson%2C%20a%20computer%20scientist%20and%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20Lastwall%2C%20a%20cybersecurity%20provider%20of%20quantum%20resilient%20technology%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20each%20company's%20announcement%20represents%20another%20building%20block%20that%20the%20industry%20will%20use%20to%20create%20a%20functioning%20quantum%20computer%20rather%20than%20a%20solution%20in%20and%20of%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20lots%20of%20challenges%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20said%20what%20Amazon%20gained%20in%20error%20correction%20with%20its%20Ocelot%20chip%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20trade-off%20for%20the%20complexity%20and%20the%20sophistication%20of%20the%20control%20systems%20and%20the%20readouts%20from%20the%20chip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERahul%20Mahajan%2C%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20the%20digital%20business%20transformation%20unit%20at%20Nagarro%2C%20a%20technological%20engineering%20and%20consulting%20firm%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20key%20to%20real%20advancement%20in%20quantum%20technology%20is%20not%20just%20about%20measuring%20or%20observing%20qubits'%20behavior%2C%20which%20the%20tech%20giants'%20recent%20papers%20largely%20focus%20on%2C%20but%20about%20reliably%20getting%20them%20to%20conduct%20the%20complex%20calculations%20they%20are%20capable%20of%20solving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20step%20is%20storing%20qubits%20and%20observing%2C%20the%20second%20is%20transformations%2C%26quot%3B%20Mahajan%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20humans%2C%20we%20evolve%3B%20in%20chemistry%2C%20molecules%20evolve%3B%20nature%20evolves.%20So%20there%20are%20simulations%20now%20for%20us%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20controlled%20simulations%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20next%20big%2C%20important%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20remaining%20hurdles%20have%20prompted%20high-profile%20skeptics%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fquantum-computing-stocks-jensen-huang-nvidia-ces-rigetti-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENvidia%20CEO%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Jensen%20Huang%20to%20suggest%20we're%20still%2020%20years%20away%20from%20the%20technology%20being%20%26quot%3Bvery%20useful.%26quot%3B%20Even%20Oskar%20Painter%2C%20the%20director%20of%20quantum%20hardware%20at%20AWS%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20when%20discussing%20the%20company's%20Ocelot%20chip%20debut%20that%20the%2020-year%20timeframe%20is%20probably%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20somewhere%20in%20between%2010%20and%2020%20years%2C%20I%20have%20some%20good%20confidence%20that%20we'll%20have%20practical%2C%20useful%20quantum%20computers%20in%20that%20timeframe%2C%26quot%3B%20Painter%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20also%20need%20to%20take%20a%20sort%20of%20humble%20and%20realistic%20approach%20to%20the%20work%20we%20have%20to%20do%20going%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c355e1e5-5ee6-47d2-bdbf-e237b410b832%5C%22%3EPrevious%20retractions%20of%20research%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft-backed%20researchers%20have%20been%20wrong%20about%20quantum%20computing%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20papers%20published%20in%20Nature%20by%20Microsoft-funded%20researchers%20in%202017%20and%202018%2C%20which%20claimed%20to%20have%20created%20similar%20Majorana%20states%20as%20the%20company's%20latest%20announcement%20about%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-microsoft-new-majorana-chip-quantum-breakthrough-state-matter-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMajorana%201%20chip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20were%20later%20retracted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Microsoft's%20latest%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D2fee788c90c1f304dc53153501ca36853216e7911ca88bb15211fe38247cb42d%26postID%3D67b927415794bed7386f4635%26postSlug%3Dscientists-say-major-quantum-computing-breakthroughs-are-years-away-2025-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.nature.com%252Farticles%252Fs41586-024-08445-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENature%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0paper%C2%A0about%20its%20recent%20Majorana%20findings%2C%20a%20passage%20in%20its%20peer-review%20file%20suggests%20the%20journal's%20editorial%20was%20still%20skeptical%20of%20the%20company's%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20editorial%20team%20wishes%20to%20point%20out%20that%20the%20results%20in%20this%20manuscript%20do%20not%20represent%20evidence%20for%20the%20presence%20of%20Majorana%20zero%20modes%20in%20the%20reported%20devices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-content.springer.com%2Fesm%2Fart%253A10.1038%252Fs41586-024-08445-2%2FMediaObjects%2F41586_2024_8445_MOESM2_ESM.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeer%20review%20file%3C%2Fa%3E%20reads.%20%26quot%3BThe%20work%20is%20published%20for%20introducing%20a%20device%20architecture%20that%20might%20enable%20fusion%20experiments%20using%20future%20Majorana%20zero%20modes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Microsoft%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20has%20received%20some%20general%20questions%20about%20its%20methodology%20since%20its%20most%20recent%20Nature%20paper%20was%20released.%20They%20said%20that%20Microsoft%20has%20continued%20advancing%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-doubles-down-quantum-computing-latest-reorg-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equantum%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20paper%20was%20first%20submitted%20on%20March%205%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiscourse%20and%20skepticism%20are%20all%20part%20of%20the%20scientific%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20we%20are%20dedicated%20to%20the%20continued%20open%20publication%20of%20our%20research%2C%20so%20that%20everyone%20can%20build%20on%20what%20others%20have%20discovered%20and%20learned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20science%20to%20explain%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20quantum%20computing%2C%20and%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks%20and%20months%2C%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20sharing%20our%20results%20along%20with%20additional%20data%20behind%20the%20science%20that%20is%20turning%20our%2020-plus-year%20vision%20for%20quantum%20computing%20into%20a%20tangible%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20leading%20quantum%20physicist%20and%20CEO%20of%20a%20quantum%20software%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Microsoft's%20claim%20of%20inventing%20a%20new%20state%20of%20topological%20matter%20amounts%20to%20little%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-major-impact-marketing-citi-cmo-alex-craddock-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarketing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20to%20prevent%20their%20skepticism%20of%20Microsoft's%20announcement%20from%20causing%20backlash%20on%20their%20own%20company%3B%20BI%20has%20verified%20their%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20important%20distinction%20that%20there%20is%20no%20topological%20quantum%20computer%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20quantum%20physicist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20buzz%20around%20the%20advancement%20of%20quantum%20computing%20is%20a%20net%20positive%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-research-execs-reveal-how-they-use-ai-daily-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearchers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20if%20the%20announcements%20from%20the%20tech%20giants%20don't%20pan%20out%20scientifically%2C%20Lorenz%2C%20the%20physics%20professor%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20self-feeding%20cycle%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Falphabet-stock-price-google-quantum-computing-breakthrough-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20means%20more%20interest%2C%20which%20means%20more%20capability%20and%20more%20promise%2C%20you%20know%3F%26quot%3B%20Lorenz%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20thi