0and%20Unnao%20are%20passing%20the%20buck%20and%20citing%20jurisdiction%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Altaf's%20family%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20tailor%20in%20Thane%20and%20came%20home%20last%20year%20after%20his%20mother's%20death.%20The%20family%20then%20asked%20him%20to%20stay%20and%20work%20in%20Unnao.%20Soon%20after%2C%20he%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20a%20married%20woman%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%20When%20his%20family%20found%20out%2C%20they%20rebuked%20him%20and%20sent%20him%20back%20to%20Thane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20woman%20kept%20torturing%20him%20even%20after%20he%20left.%20She%20told%20him%20that%20she%20was%20pregnant%20and%20asked%20for%20money.%20Her%20demands%20ranged%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20She%20threatened%20him%20with%20a%20false%20case%20and%20jail%20term.%20He%20was%20forced%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%2C%26quot%3B%20Altaf's%20sister%20Reshma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20before%20his%20death%2C%20Altaf%20video-called%20the%20woman%20and%20told%20her%20that%20he%20was%20suffering%20because%20of%20her.%20%26quot%3BShe%20told%20him%20that%20she%20has%20her%20husband%20and%20would%20lose%20nothing%20if%20he%20died.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20days%20after%20Altaf's%20death%2C%20Maharashtra%20Police%20informed%20the%20family.%20The%20family%20left%20for%20Thane%20and%20buried%20him%20there.%20%26quot%3BWe%20found%20later%20that%20this%20woman%20had%20been%20harassing%20and%20blackmailing%20him%20and%20he%20was%20so%20upset%20that%20he%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%26quot%3B%20Reshma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20family%20had%20approached%20Maharashtra%20police%2C%20but%20they%20said%20the%20matter%20comes%20under%20Unnao%20police.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20returned%20and%20went%20to%20the%20local%20police%20station%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%2C%20we%20were%20told%20to%20get%20it%20registered%20in%20Maharashtra.%20We%20had%20even%20caught%20the%20woman%20an