0tech%20company.%20My%20tenure%20at%20McKinsey%20strengthened%20my%20ability%20to%20build%20relationships%20in%20professional%20environments%2C%20a%20skill%20that%20has%20helped%20me%20throughout%20my%20career.%20I've%20also%20been%20using%20a%20fun%20term%20to%20describe%20this%20skill%3A%20biz%20rizz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220a62cec7-f1b0-4a6d-80d7-f815d1ee3bfe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMentors%20helped%20me%20with%20relationship-building%20skills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20at%20McKinsey%2C%20I%20was%20linked%20up%20with%20a%20professional%20development%20manager%20who%20helped%20staff%20me%20on%20projects.%20In%20consulting%2C%20you%20don't%20really%20have%20a%20set%20manager%20and%20team%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20all%20project-based.%20Every%20few%20weeks%20or%20months%2C%20you're%20working%20with%20new%20people%2C%20clients%2C%20and%20often%20in%20new%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20obviously%20hard%20skills%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-firms-sponsors-secret-to-success-mckinsey-accenture-consultants-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsultants%20should%20have%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20making%20Excel%20models%20and%20analysis%2C%20but%20also%20soft%20skills%20%E2%80%94%20the%20ability%20to%20build%20relationships%20with%20clients.%20Some%20of%20this%20was%20formally%20taught%2C%20such%20as%20in%20a%20training%20session%20about%20trust%2C%20but%20I%20also%20developed%20soft%20skills%20organically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20biggest%20barriers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-to-build-strong-and-authentic-relationships-at-work-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloping%20relationships%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20confidence%20and%20comfort.%20At%20McKinsey%2C%20you%20can%20be%2021%20sitting%20in%20a%20room%20with%20C-Suite%20executives%2C%20which%20can%20be%20intimidating.%20You%20overthink%20in%20those%20situations%20about%20what's%20appropriate%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20parents%20found%20out%20I%20had%20this%20job%2C%20they%20advised%20me%20to%20keep%20my%20head%20down%2C%20but%20I%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-relationships-with-coworkers-from-home-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprofessional%20relationship-building%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20important.%20I%20tried%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20network%20and%20make%20small%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20lucky%20to%20have%20great%20mentors%20on%20my%20first%20projects.%20One%20of%20my%20managers%20coached%20me%20to%20present%20to%20a%20C-suite%20executive.%20One%20of%20my%20mentors%20told%20me%20to%20think%20about%20the%20executive%20as%20my%20friend's%20uncle%20or%20someone%20I%20know%20in%20real%20life%20to%20make%20things%20feel%20more%20familiar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20struggled%20to%20relate%20during%20some%20conversations%20with%20my%20peers.%20Travel%20came%20up%20a%20lot%3B%20I%20didn't%20grow%20up%20skiing%20in%20the%20Alps%20or%20playing%20golf.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-i-go-business-school-deep-dive-into-pros-cons-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoing%20to%20business%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%20train%20me%20for%20these%20conversations%2C%20and%20my%20background%20wasn't%20as%20big%20of%20a%20constraint%20as%20I%20thought.%20I%20think%20the%20key%20is%20to%20be%20authentically%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2281f36dd7-6a32-4ace-bb42-877199b37ca4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaving%20'biz%20rizz'%20has%20helped%20me%20throughout%20my%20career%20so%20far%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20feedback%20from%20the%20teams%20I%20worked%20with%20to%20gauge%20how%20well%20I%20was%20developing%20my%20relationship-building%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20project%2C%20I%20was%20tasked%20with%20preparing%20a%20celebration%20at%20the%20end%20of%20our%20off-site.%20It%20was%20a%20circle%20of%20appreciation.%20Everyone%20had%20to%20say%20what%20they%20appreciated%20about%20someone%20they%20were%20assigned%2C%20like%20a%20secret%20Santa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wrote%20a%20funny%20poem%20with%20silly%20rhymes%20about%20the%20person%20I%20was%20assigned%2C%20who%20was%20a%20client.%20I%20was%20more%20experienced%20at%20that%20point%2C%20so%20could%20confidently%20gauge%20what%20was%20appropriate.%20Earlier%20in%20my%20career%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20done%20something%20like%20that.%20Afterward%2C%20the%20key%20stakeholder%20from%20that%20client%20referenced%20the%20poem%20for%20months%20after%20the%20off-site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoft-skills-leaders-need-for-success-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESoft%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20this%20can%20strengthen%20your%20reputation%20and%20relationships%20at%20work.%20They%20have%20been%20helpful%20beyond%20my%20time%20at%20McKinsey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20previous%20job%2C%20I%20was%20a%20director%20of%20strategy%20and%20business%20operations%20for%20a%20tech%20company.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20facilitate%20change%20management%20and%20worked%20with%20leaders%20across%20different%20functions.%20You%20have%20to%20build%20trust-based%20relationships%20to%20get%20people%20to%20align%20with%20your%20vision.%20This%20can%20be%20hard%20when%20you're%20younger%20or%20new%2C%20but%20my%20time%20at%20McKinsey%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20engage%20with%20senior%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20times%20when%20I've%20done%20coffee%20chats%20or%20mentorship%20sessions%20with%20students%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20questions%20are%20about%20what%20grades%20they%20need%20or%20tactical%20skills%20they%20should%20build%20to%20get%20a%20certain%20job.%20That's%20all%20important%2C%20but%20another%20really%20important%20part%20is%20how%20you%20network%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-build-pe