22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI've%20Seen%20Him%26quot%3B%3A%20UP%20Speaker%20Slams%20MLA%20For%20Spitting%20'Pan%20Masala'%20In%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Satish%20Mahana%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20that%20some%20Assembly%20members%20spit%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20hall%20after%20consuming%20pan%20masala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20members%20before%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20House%20today%2C%20Mahana%20revealed%20that%20he%20personally%20cleaned%20the%20area%20after%20receiving%20information%20about%20the%20incident.%20While%20he%20acknowledged%20having%20seen%20the%20MLA%20involved%20in%20the%20act%20through%20a%20video%2C%20he%20refrained%20from%20naming%20the%20individual%20to%20avoid%20public%20humiliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20morning%2C%20I%20received%20information%20that%20in%20this%20hall%20of%20our%20Vidhan%20Sabha%2C%20some%20Member%20has%20spit%20after%20consuming%20pan%20masala.%20So%2C%20I%20came%20here%20and%20got%20it%20cleaned.%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20MLA%20in%20the%20video.%20But%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20humiliate%20any%20individual.%20So%2C%20I%20am%20not%20taking%20their%20name.%20I%20urge%20all%20Members%20that%20if%20they%20see%20anyone%20doing%20this%2C%20they%20should%20stop%20them...Keeping%20this%20Assembly%20clean%20is%20our%20responsibility...If%20the%20MLA%20in%20question%20comes%20and%20tells%20me%20that%20they%20have%20done%20this%2C%20it%20will%20be%20good%3B%20otherwise%2C%20I%20will%20call%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Finance%20Minister%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Khanna%20on%20February%2020%20presented%20state%20budget%20for%20the%20year%202025-26.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20asserted%20that%20the%20state's%20budget%20is%209.8%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20the%202024-25%20budget%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20CM%20Yogi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20budget%20is%20over%208%2C08%2C736%20crore%20Rs%2C%20which%20is%209.8%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20the%202024-25%20budget.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20growth%20in%20the%20budget%20size%20reflects%20the%20state's%20strength%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20also%20shows%20the%20commitment%20of%20the%20double-engine%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20highlighted%20that%20while%20UP's%20economy%20was%20previously%20ranked%206th-7th%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%20is%20now%20the%20second-largest%20economy%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20report%20by%20NITI%20Aayog%20on%20the%20fiscal%20health%20of%20states%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20front-runner%20category.%20Between%202018%20and%202022%2C%20the%20state's%20physical%20health%20index%20increased%20by%208.9%20per%20cent%2C%20and%20during%20this%20period%2C%20UP%20succeeded%20in%20reducing%20unemployment%20and%20creating%20additional%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B22%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20budget%20has%20been%20allocated%20to%20infrastructure%20development.%20For%20education%2C%201%2C06%2C360%20crore%20Rs%20has%20been%20allocated%2C%20which%20is%2013%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20budget.%20While%20there%20is%20usually%20a%206%20per%20cent%20demand%20for%20education%2C%20UP%20is%20one%20of%20the%20states%20in%20the%20country%20that%20spends%2013%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20budget%20on%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20CM%20Yogi%20emphasized.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20CM%20also%20outlined%20that%2011%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20budget%20has%20been%20proposed%20for%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20healthcare%2C%20the%20government%20has%20allocated%2050%20thousand%20550%20crore%20Rs%2C%20which%20is%206%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20budget.%20For%20the%20Social%2