icut-governor-concludes-economic-mission-to-india-strengthens-business-ties%2Famp_articleshow%2F118699018.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20is%20beating%20its%20military%20recruitment%20goals%20as%20Putin%20pumps%20cash%20into%20bonuses%20and%20lets%20men%20sign%20up%20to%20avoid%20trials%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20soldiers%20march%20during%20the%20Victory%20Day%20military%20parade%20dress%20rehearsal%20at%20the%20Red%20Square%20in%20Moscow%20in%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a976ff6630eb10385c0c42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20recruitment%20is%20still%20going%20strong%20into%202025%2C%20and%20Ukraine%20expects%20Moscow%20to%20keep%20hiring%20people%20straight%20out%20of%20criminal%20trials%2C%20a%20top%20intelligence%20official%20said.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FAlexander%20Zemlianichenko%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20top%20Ukrainian%20official%20said%20Russia%20beat%20its%202024%20recruitment%20goal%20and%20is%20still%20doing%20so%20in%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20after%20Moscow%20already%20raised%20its%20goal%20to%20430%2C000%20troops%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20comes%20as%20Russia%20has%20poured%20cash%20into%20sign-up%20bonuses%20and%20passed%20laws%20to%20recruit%20crime%20suspects.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20chief%20of%20Ukraine's%20military%20intelligence%20said%20Russia%20is%20exceeding%20its%20recruitment%20targets%2C%20affirming%20Moscow's%20earlier%20claim%20of%20hiring%20over%20440%2C000%20soldiers%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20recruiting%20success%20is%20set%20to%20continue%20in%202025%2C%20Maj.%20Gen.%20Vadim%20Skibitsky%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20published%20by%20the%20news%20agency%20RBC%20Ukraine%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20January%2C%20they%20fulfilled%20their%20recruitment%20plans%20by%20107%25%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Skibitsky.%20%26quot%3BThis%20issue%20remains%20relevant%2C%20and%20the%20Russian%20authorities%20have%20no%20problem%20with%20staffing%20their%20troops%20and%20filling%20losses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkibitsky%20said%20Russia%20initially%20set%20a%20hiring%20target%20of%20380%2C000%20troops%20in%202024%20but%20raised%20it%20to%20430%2C000%20recruits.%20And%20beat%20that%20goal%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Dmitry%20Medvedev%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20Russia's%20security%20council%2C%20said%20Moscow%20had%20signed%20contracts%20with%20440%2C000%20new%20soldiers%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkibitsky%20confirmed%20that%20number%20in%20his%20Monday%20interview%20and%20said%20that%20Russia%20officially%20plans%20to%20recruit%20another%20343%2C000%20soldiers%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20based%20on%20the%20experience%20of%202024%2C%20we%20know%20that%20these%20plans%20inevitably%20change%2C%20in%20the%20upward%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecruiting%20at%20that%20scale%20is%20allowing%20Russia%20to%20continue%20fighting%20intensely%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Skibitsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20almost%2080%25%20of%20those%20recruited%20under%20contract%20are%20used%20to%20replace%20combat%20losses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20RBC%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20reported%20figures%20come%20as%20the%20Kremlin%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-military-troops-new-recruits-ukraine-bonus-high-death-rate-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epoured%20cash%20into%20one-time%20recruitment%20bonuses%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20military%20%E2%80%94%20just%20one%20of%20many%20ways%20it's%20pushing%20its%20economy%20and%20spending%20toward%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Russian%20leader%20Vladimir%20Putin%20signed%20a%20decree%20that%20more%20than%20doubled%20the%20baseline%20sign-up%20bonus%20from%20195%2C000%20rubles%20to%20400%2C000%20rubles%20for%20the%20rest%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20400%2C000%20ruble%20payout%20is%20worth%20about%20%244%2C450%20now.%20But%20some%20regions%20upped%20their%20bonuses%20to%20nearly%202%20million%20rubles%20last%20year%2C%20putting%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-sign-up-bonuses-reaching-on-par-with-us-military-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20par%20with%20the%20US%20military's%20sign-on%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20Russian%20Federation%2C%20these%20are%20very%20large%20sums%2C%26quot%3B%20Skibitsky%20told%20RBC%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFederal%20statistics%20from%20the%20Russian%20government%20in%20December%20cited%20the%20average%20monthly%20wage%20in%20the%20country%20as%2086%2C500%20rubles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20expects%20Russia%20to%20also%20significantly%20ramp%20up%20the%20number%20of%20soldiers%20it%20recruits%20from%20prisons%20or%20criminal%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Russia%20already%20actively%20recruiting%20from%20prisons%2C%20Putin%20signed%20a%20bill%20in%20October%20allowing%20those%20who%20face%20criminal%20charges%20to%20avoid%20their%20trials%20or%20convictions%20if%20they%20enlist%20in%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkibitsky%20said%20Russia's%20plans%20for%202025%20include%2030%25%20of%20its%20forces%20being%20made%20up%20of%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20contingents%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20describe%20units%20fielding%20inmates%20or%20soldiers%20who%20signed%20up%20to%20avoid%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20up%20from%2015%25%20of%20its%20forces%20involving%20such%20troops%20last%20year%2C%20Skibitsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20issue%20is%20already%20arising%20for%20the%20General%20Staff%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20of%20the%20Russian%20Federation%20%E2%80%94%20what%20to%20do%20with%20these%20people%20and%20how%20to%20work%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C