0female%20freediver%2C%20radiating%20courage%2C%20determination%2C%20and%20profound%20connection%20with%20the%20underwater%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChoosing%20the%20%E2%80%98easiest%E2%80%99%20professional%20degree%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchana%E2%80%99s%20path%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20so%20clear.%20After%20completing%20her%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20in%20commerce%20from%20RD%20National%20College%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20a%20brief%20stint%20with%20the%20CA%20exams%2C%20she%20understood%20the%20difficulties%20in%20cracking%20it%20despite%20clearing%20the%20MCQs%20on%20her%20first%20attempt.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20was%20hopeful%20that%20I%20would%20clear%20the%20final%20exams%20as%20well%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20with%20complete%20confidence%20that%20I%20could%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20quips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20might%20sound%20absurd%2C%20but%20since%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20out%20of%20CA%2C%20I%20looked%20into%20the%20easiest%20professional%20degree%20I%20could%20obtain.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20law%2C%20a%20decision%20driven%20more%20by%20practicality%20than%20passion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20successful%20entrance%20exam%20secured%20her%20a%20place%20at%20the%20same%20college%20where%20she%20did%20her%20undergraduate%20studies.%20The%20ambition%20then%20was%20clear%3A%20a%20coveted%20position%20at%20a%20top-tier%20law%20firm.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20point%2C%20all%20I%20wanted%20was%20to%20get%20into%20a%20Tier-I%20law%20firm%20because%20that%20meant%20I%20was%20sorted%20for%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20An%20internship%20at%20AZB%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20parale